SUBCONTRACT AGREEMENT
Plumbing Works
Agreement Date: 5 July 2024
Project: New Dwelling - 123 Sunset Boulevard, Sydney NSW
Principal Contractor:
ABC Construction Pty Ltd | ABN: 12 345 678 901 | License: 123456C
Subcontractor:
John's Plumbing Services Pty Ltd | ABN: 55 667 889 001 | License: PL-234567
WORKS TO BE PERFORMED:
Complete plumbing installation including:
• Cold and hot water supply systems (copper and PEX pipe)
• Sanitary drainage (PVC 100mm and 150mm)
• Stormwater drainage and connection to Council system
• Installation of fixtures: toilets, basins, showers, bath, kitchen sink
• Hot water system connection (315L electric storage)
• Backflow prevention devices
• Pressure testing and certification to AS/NZS 3500
CONTRACT SUM: $19,150.00 (inc GST)
PAYMENT SCHEDULE:
• Monthly progress claims based on work completed
• Payment within 30 days of approved claim
• 5% retention until final completion + 90 days
PROGRAM:
Start: 20 July 2024 | Completion: 25 September 2024
Agreed and Acce
